OWESIFAZANE ongowokudabuka eZimbabwe, uFungai Nyamadzawo, osolwa ngokubulala indodakazi yakhe eneminyaka eyisithupha u-Alexia Nyamadzawo, unomlando wokuphazamiseka emqondweni. Lokhu kuvele namhlanje enkantolo yeMantshi eMhlali njengoba ebevele okwesibili ngaleli cala. Bekulindeleke ukuthi afake isicelo sebheyile kodwa uMshushisi kuleli cala uSanesh Rambaran utshele iMantshi uBlanche van Eeden ukuthi sebethole imininingwane emisha ekhomba ukuthi umsolwa unomlando wokuphazamiseka emqondweni. Kule nkantolo kuvele ukuthi kunemibiko yodokotela emayelana nalokhu. Ukuvela kwale mininingwane kungenzeka kuphoqe ukuthi lo wesifazane oneminyaka ewu-42, kudingeke ayohlolwa esikhungweni sezempilo ukuqinisekisa ukuthi angakwazi yini ukumelana necala asolwa ngalo. Iisdumbu sikaAlexia satholwa ngamaphoyisa ehlathini ngemuva kokuthi unina ebike ukuthi indodakazi yakhe ithunjwe wumuntu ongaziwa, oyihlwithe emotweni yalo wesifazane eGlandale. Le ntombazanyana yagcwala ezinkundleni zokuxhumana njengoba yayibikwa njengomuntu owayelahlekile, kodwa ngemuva kwezinsuku, kwaboshwa unina. Lo wesifazane kulindeleke ukuthi aphinde avele enkantolo ngoJune 17, kanti uzoqhubeka nokugqunywa esitokisini. 